Eugene had fathered
three other children.

1006
00:41:38,830 --> 00:41:39,904
(crowd murmuring)

1007
00:41:40,073 --> 00:41:41,831
And they're here with us today.

1008
00:41:42,058 --> 00:41:45,484
God, he sees all,

1009
00:41:45,653 --> 00:41:47,170
and he forgives all.

1010
00:41:47,339 --> 00:41:49,564
- Eugene. (chuckles)
- (mutters)

