he forgives him.

1014
00:41:58,800 --> 00:42:00,850
Oh, now that's
true Christianity.

1015
00:42:01,077 --> 00:42:03,244
Judge not lest ye be judged.

1016
00:42:03,413 --> 00:42:04,832
That's what the Reverend
told me,

1017
00:42:04,856 --> 00:42:06,414
