who stays,

1021
00:42:14,866 --> 00:42:16,849
so with the Lord's guidance,

1022
00:42:17,018 --> 00:42:20,762
I welcome Antonio Rivera,
Jason Conley,

1023
00:42:20,930 --> 00:42:22,855
and Ginger Sweet to ours.

